sysevent_email_action.message:
Dear ${requested_for.first_name},

Your employee ${request_type} request has been successfully submitted and is now pending manager approval.

REQUEST DETAILS:
================
Employee Name:    ${employee_full_name}
Employee ID:      ${employee_id}
Department:       ${department}
Request Type:     ${request_type}
Submitted On:     ${sys_created_on}
Reference Number: ${number}

WHAT HAPPENS NEXT:
==================
1. Your manager will receive an approval request via email
2. Upon approval, tasks will be automatically assigned to HR, IT, Facilities, and Security teams
3. You will receive a notification once all tasks are completed

Please contact HR if you need assistance: hr@skillwallet.com

Best regards,
HR Automation System - SKILLWALLET

Dear ${manager.first_name},

An employee ${request_type} request requires your approval.

EMPLOYEE DETAILS:
=================
Employee Name:    ${employee_full_name}
Employee ID:      ${employee_id}
Department:       ${department}
Request Type:     ${request_type}
Joining Date:     ${joining_date}
Exit Date:        ${exit_date}
Submitted On:     ${sys_created_on}

TO APPROVE OR REJECT:
=====================
Please log in to ServiceNow and navigate to the approval record to approve or reject this request.
Direct Link: ${approval_link}

IMPORTANT: This approval must be completed within 3 business days.

For questions, please contact HR: hr@skillwallet.com

Best regards,
HR Automation System - SKILLWALLET

Dear Team,

The employee ${request_type} request has been approved. Departmental tasks have been automatically created and assigned.

EMPLOYEE INFORMATION:
=====================
Employee Name:    ${employee_full_name}
Employee ID:      ${employee_id}
Department:       ${department}
Request Type:     ${request_type}
Approved By:      ${approver}
Approval Date:    ${approval_date}

TASKS CREATED FOR:
==================
- HR Department: Employee records, documentation, payroll
- IT Department: System access, hardware, accounts
- Facilities Department: Workspace, keys, parking
- Security Department: Access badge, building permissions

Please complete your assigned tasks promptly.

HR Automation System - SKILLWALLET

Dear ${requested_for.first_name},

We are pleased to confirm that the employee ${request_type} process has been successfully completed.

COMPLETION SUMMARY:
===================
Employee Name:      ${employee_full_name}
Employee ID:        ${employee_id}
Department:         ${department}
Request Type:       ${request_type}
Completion Date:    ${sys_updated_on}
Reference Number:   ${number}

COMPLETED TASKS:
================
✓ HR - Employee records, documentation, payroll updated
✓ IT - System access and hardware provisioned/deprovisioned
✓ Facilities - Workspace and keys prepared/returned
✓ Security - Access badges and building permissions configured

${onboarding_message}

If you have any questions, please contact HR: hr@skillwallet.com

Best regards,
HR Automation System - SKILLWALLET

Dear ${requested_for.first_name},

Unfortunately, your employee ${request_type} request has been rejected.

REQUEST DETAILS:
================
Employee Name:    ${employee_full_name}
Employee ID:      ${employee_id}
Department:       ${department}
Request Type:     ${request_type}
Rejected By:      ${approver}
Rejection Date:   ${updated_on}
Rejection Reason: ${comments}

NEXT STEPS:
===========
Please contact your HR department or your manager for further clarification regarding this rejection.

HR Contact: hr@skillwallet.com

Best regards,
HR Automation System - SKILLWALLET
